sts, we show that, despite some caveats, the existence of GJ 581g remains the\nmost likely orbital solution to the currently available RV data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Oct 2010 18:14:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2011 20:05:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-05-03"}
