rror term in the sharp Weyl theorem. The proof of our\nresult uses a recent estimate of the first author \\cite{Sokakeya} that gives a\nnecessary and sufficient condition that\n$\\|e_\\lambda\\|_{L^4(M)}=o(\\lambda^{1/8})$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Oct 2010 22:55:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-29"}
