 to be an accurate approximation only when N_e s^2 << 1,\nwhere N_e is the effective population size.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2010 14:02:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2011 11:52:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-22"}
